{{wikipediapar|Deism}}
==English==

===Etymology===
From {{L.}} ''[[deus]]'', "god".

===Noun===
{{en-noun-unc}}

# {{philosophy}} The [[belief]] in the [[existence]] of [[God]], especially by or through [[reason]].
# The belief in a God who set the universe in motion, then ceased to interact with it.

